Purpose
========================================
  A system able to generate a skeleton for program/script files.  Works off of a templated system of some type (XML or some other format).


Requirements
========================================
Needs to be very portable.  Perl is probably the most widely available scripting language.

Supported types:
	windows batch
	unix shell
	perl

Enhancements
========================================
Optionally supported types?
	powershell
	python
	html
	css
	php

Thoughts on template system?




General Format
(modeled with the number sign (#) as the comment marker)
         1         2         3         4         5         6         7         8
12345678901234567890123456789012345678901234567890123456789012345678901234567890
############################################################
#
#  Program Name     :
#  Purpose          :
#  Version          :
#  Associated Files :
#
############################################################
#  History
#  yyyymmdd   username   version   comment   (example line)
#  20120416   abcdwxyz   1.00.00   Created.
#
############################################################
